{"tid":466170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婆幹-婆婆擬600萬買薈蕎助18歲孫置業","createTime":"2017-11-12T09:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T05:19:34.000Z","uid":72009,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e190a3ee4cedbb38d4b40913e1c49031d0228518","tid":466170,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:54:18.000Z","msg":"宏安地產（1243）旗下「迷你豪宅」大圍薈蕎，周四高價開售之後，昨首度開放示範單位，並即日進行收票，發展商指昨首日收約140票，較公佈首張68伙價單超額認購1倍。<br />\n<br />\n睇樓客嫌開價太貴<br />\n<br />\n記者昨天約下午3時到示範單位觀察，睇樓人潮並不太多，大約排隊10分鐘便可以入內參觀。宏安於晚上9時宣佈，薈蕎首天收140票，錄得1,300參觀人次。 <br />\n英皇國際（0163）執行董事張炳強亦有到場打氣，沒發表言論便離開。宏安行政總裁黃耀雄滿意昨日參觀情況，並對銷情甚具信心。部份睇樓客嫌開價太貴，直指兩房賣600萬元才算合理。<br />\n睇客樓中包括沙田街坊陳婆婆（圓圖），她預算用600萬元買2房單位，幫助現時在英國讀書的18歲孫仔置業，認為現時上車難，年輕人要屋企人幫手。<br />\n市場消息指出，截至傍晚近6時，一手市場暫錄得約13宗成交，馬頭角君柏、何文田皓畋及元朗Park Yoho各有3宗成交，一切以一手成交冊公佈為準。一手成交冊顯示，華懋的九龍塘雲門錄得一宗成交，為2座10樓B室，連1個車位以5,259.25萬元易手，呎價4.17萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171112/large/12ls8p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171112%2Flarge%2F12ls8p10.jpg&h=1dcbcdf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5bf4231fe176143c867797a4de1093afa4884e","tid":466170,"uid":51978,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"個盤名做乜事 食得㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4123f2a1a6a237743da116ae741cc5bfd8984e2","tid":466170,"uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個盤名做乜事 食得㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留學返來即有炮房<br />\n日日約女同事打炮<br />\n理忍甚麼名"},{"pid":"6cc68254fe5779a9ce0033821ea68717d70138fe","tid":466170,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:01:14.000Z","msg":"感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9064b8b742c9c7bb98ff4105019e15b47bff98b4","tid":466170,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:04:02.000Z","msg":"婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ec3bfcf261e8d0739bf5c186887460d2da23c3","tid":466170,"uid":32577,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:06:25.000Z","msg":"婆婆，我係你失散多年既孫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1e06cd6d7678e012b51a38efd3fd86839ab70e","tid":466170,"uid":91156,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:24:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d75e63762c5829288be8bac2290d51af78141c3","tid":466170,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:46:31.000Z","msg":"個盤名好驅風呀"},{"pid":"a99e50c81d191085e78d66c8135edb9bef5cd3d5","tid":466170,"uid":10692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d33600ca3b42812b018c1013b189cb1b6b9b6795","tid":466170,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:32:01.000Z","msg":"薈蕎位於大埔公路-大圍段7838號，前方為沙田嶺道8號的戈林，物業同屬宏安發展，惟屬面積逾2,000方呎洋房，昔日新界半山區多建大面積豪宅，今日則因應市場上車需要，由「劏房」新盤佔據。<br />\n<br />\n薈蕎地勢於大圍半山，遠望寶福紀念館，鄰近富山公眾殮房，地勢較高地方為火葬場。物業仍在興建階段，全幢分1翼及2翼分佈單位，全層共32伙，只有四部電梯，預計2019年4月落成，尚有一年半樓花期。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e422a6e0ddaba72170eda6b688b63341cd971e5d","tid":466170,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:35:00.000Z","msg":"開放式都要四球幾"},{"pid":"db2641f073f56f00c1415822a9e34afc7b198f90","tid":466170,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:01:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開放式都要四球幾</blockquote><br />\n無中AA計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收租租唔到幾$<br />\n<br />\n租到$45呎 先有2.5%<br />\n放銀行好過"},{"pid":"58c178b2b656c4b28df6431c06937f5ebc12fdbf","tid":466170,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>婆婆，我係你失散多年既孫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n婆婆，我都係你失散多年既孫呀.........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n婆婆，我係你老公呀"},{"pid":"abccc74ded447877891ac42ad2010788b5cb0b6e","tid":466170,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>婆婆，我係你失散多年既孫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n婆婆，我都係你失散多年既孫呀.........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n婆婆，我係你老公呀</blockquote><br />\n婆婆: 咁你仲唔俾錢?"},{"pid":"bb950ea78536864a5437492b82f7ae41f1bd7794","tid":466170,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:23:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開放式都要四球幾</blockquote><br />\n無中AA計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收租租唔到幾$<br />\n<br />\n租到$45呎 先有2.5%<br />\n放銀行好過</blockquote><br />\n呢個盤係幾靜下<br />\n之前果d納米樓受歡迎係因為lump sum細 三球幾好多捧場客 呢d盤揀樓當日由平單位向上掃 唔理樓層座向只睇價錢<br />\n<br />\n呢個二百零呎studio 要四百幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下場同之前薄扶林個納米盤咁"},{"pid":"0c9cb0898893bd32dd3c63c0a6fb5a98af8c11d3","tid":466170,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:26:42.000Z","msg":"個盤2萬蚊呎 已經唔係貴 係on撚9"},{"pid":"958f54c84f2a69c76a162f6e87e50b600d0c1dfb","tid":466170,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/1945703/%E3%80%90%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E3%80%91%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E8%96%88%E8%95%8E%E6%9A%AB%E6%94%B6%E7%B4%84150%E7%A5%A8%20%E8%B6%85%E9%A1%8D%E9%80%BE%E5%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1945703%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258D%25E8%2596%2588%25E8%2595%258E%25E6%259A%25AB%25E6%2594%25B6%25E7%25B4%2584150%25E7%25A5%25A8%2520%25E8%25B6%2585%25E9%25A1%258D%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%2580%258D&d=GDco4eikgCNzwlCeCv518gCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=52712c82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/1945703/%E3%80%90%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E3%80%91%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E8%96%88%E8%95%8E%E6%9A%AB%E6%94%B6%E7%B4%84150%E7%A5%A8%20%E8%B6%85%E9%A1%8D%E9%80%BE%E5%80%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n68伙收得150飛<br />\n近排過4m既細碼一手盤個勢都.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82dbb518f00885a7c3d0d6fdde6d32c232659362","tid":466170,"uid":19